This project includes modifications and improvements to the original EF_SPI
design, including but not limited to:
- Renamed modules and files from EF_SPI to CF_SPI
- Updated documentation and configuration files
- Modified copyright notices and attribution
- Updated repository references and URLs
- Enhanced bus wrapper implementations for APB, AHB-Lite, and Wishbone
- Improved UVM testbench with comprehensive verification coverage
- Added DFT (Design for Test) support in bus wrappers

